Package: ebox-antivirus
Architecture: all
Depends: ebox (>= 1.1), ebox (<< 1.2), ebox-firewall, clamav (>= 0.90), clamav-daemon (>= 0.90), clamav-freshclam (>= 0.90), ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: ebox (<< 0.11.99)
Description: eBox - Antivirus module
 eBox is a framework for the development and deployment of security-wise
 network services in small and medium-sized networks, offering a simplified
 graphical interface to non expert users. It can be set up as a gateway,
 having some extra features over a usual router.
 .
 This module adds an antivirus scanner server to your eBox installation, allowingits use by other eBox services that needs to scan for viruses.
